data.body:
Issue arises where brackets which are part of a string or regex match up with brackets that define blocks when the language type is set to JavaScript.

`function() {
    var regex = /\sibTplLoop='(.*?})'(.*?>)/;
};`

Opening bracket of function block will match closing bracket in regex. 

1.0.0 Ubuntu 14.04 and 1.0.19 Yosemite 10.10.5
